WEBVTT

04:31.525 --> 04:33.400
I have committed seven murders.

04:36.900 --> 04:38.567
"A murderer or an Artist?"

04:39.484 --> 04:42.359
"Series of paintings
of a serial killer"

04:43.067 --> 04:46.484
"The Pattampoochi (Butterfly) flies
high while the police struggle"

04:47.859 --> 04:49.150
Your words.

04:49.734 --> 04:51.067
My actions.

04:51.775 --> 04:52.817
Pattampoochi! (Butterfly)

04:59.859 --> 05:00.942
How do I trust all this?
